  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of CDP870 and Methotrexate Compared to Methotrexate Alone in Subjects With Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of CDP870 400 mg in Combination With Methotrexate Compared to Methotrexate Alone in the Treatment of the Signs and Symptoms of Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis Who Are Partial Responders to Methotrexate</official_title>
