  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  male/female, 18-75 years old, inclusive

          -  diagnosis of adult-onset RA

          -  had active disease

          -  had received methotrexate

          -  on a stable dose of folic acid

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  contraindication for methotrexate or anti-TNF
      </textblock>
